Package com.phonytive.astive.agi

Interface Summary
AgiResponse API with all commands supported by the AGI protocol, since Asterisk version 1.0.
Connection Provide read/write capabilities for few objects.
DefaultAgiServerSettings Define few global variables for an FASTAGI server.
 

Class Summary
AgiCommandHandler Handle communication with Asterisk, in the lowest level.
AgiCommandReply  
AgiRequest Contain information about the channel the script is invoked on.
CommandProcessor This class is a helper.
Converter Perform an data conversion by using meta-data in an object.
StringConverter Convert data types use by Asterisk(Datetime, TimeZone, array, boolean, int) to text.
 

Enum Summary
ChannelStatus Enum that handle the status of a channel.
ChannelType Enum that handle the status of a channel.
HangupCause Enum that handle the hangup cause for a channel.
PresentationType Enum that map the presentation type for the callerId (@link AgiRequest).
TonType Enum that map the ton type for an incoming call.
